{
  "texts": [
    "It is worth noting that there is a minimal number of studies that have used TM technique for ASBA since 2009 as shown in Fig. 22(in appendix).",
    "This is due to options available to perform ABSA.",
    "Topic 8 accounts for 11.14% of the entire document.",
    "The documents categorised in Topic 8 are focused on mining information to support policy or implement business strategy.",
    "For example, TM techniques were used to extract topics from online education discussion forums, and student feedback (Hynninen et al. 2019; Parsa and Golab 2021; Nunes et al. 2014a, b; Shafana and Safnas 2022), to support education policy decision-making and curriculum development."
  ]
}